description.text:
Creates a patio paver of the interlocking octagonal and square style
Parameter list:<br />
//side - length of the sides of the octagonal and square<br />
//diag - length of the diagonals of the octagonal<br />
//brickheight - height of a brick, min 2 for things to work correctly<br />
//bevel - how far the top of the simple 45 degree bevel is inset, overly large values will cause odd results<br />
//Octagonal brick bottom will be at the origin and the square part will go in the +x direction
